SUMMARY:Screaming Daisies @ Burning Bridge Wrightsville
DESCRIPTION:Meet People Lancaster\nDo you like rock music? Come jam & danc
 e with us!\n\nWe will meet in the bar area at 7pm on Saturday\, March 21st
  - the band starts playing at 8pm til 11pm! Central PA SOLOs group will be
  joining us.\n\nLocation: Burning Bridge Wrightsville - 108 Hellam Street 
 #1310\, Wrightsville PA 17638\n\nHost: Chris Rohrbaugh\n\n**if anyone can 
 help me save tables\, please let me know in the comments below
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/meet-people-lancaster/events/31377928
 4/
